      <title>韩国首次因医生罢工而吊销执照</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/south-korea-issues-first-license-suspension-for-doctors-walkout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国当局已发出通知，暂时吊销两名医生的执照，这是自大约一个月前实习医生因抗议政府增加医学院入学人数的计划而罢工以来的首次处罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/south-korea-issues-first-license-suspension-for-doctors-walkout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 05:39:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
